TEXT.TITLE: WELBILT <WELB> COMPLETES ACQUISITIONS
TEXT.BODY: Welbilt Corp said it completed the previously announced acquisitions of the assets of L and M Manufacturing Co and Food Machinery Engineering Co, two manufacturers of automated bakery production equipment headquartered in Toronto. Reuter
